Package: libyacjp-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libyacjp (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Yet Another C-JSON Parser
 A JSON parser and pretty printer written in C, with a modular
 structure.
 Also provides an all-purpose hash table, utf-8 input/output streams,
 and utf-16/32 to utf-8 input streams.

